  "texts": [
    "The following are equivalent:1.",
    "⟨A, ≤⟩ is a p-semilattice such that the restriction of ≤ to A \\ {⊥} is a separative partial order; 2.",
    "⟨A, ≤⟩ is a Boolean lattice.Proof.",
    "Frink [1962] showed that ⟨A, ≤⟩ is a Boolean lattice iff ⟨A, ≤⟩ is a p-semilattice such that for all x ∈ A, x * * = x.",
